tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE qubit_states (
  qubit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  state_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE qubit_connections (
  connection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  qubit1_id INT,
  qubit2_id INT,
  connection_strength FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_systems (
  system_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  system_name TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE quantum_operations (
  operation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  operation_name TEXT,
  operation_description TEXT
)
